 3. If the issue persists after freeing up space, consider increasing the size of the tablespace. To do this, first, identify the current maximum size of the tablespace using the command "otel db query 'SELECT MAX(SIZE)/1024/1024 AS MaxSize FROM otel\_database'". Then, you can increase the size of the tablespace using the command "otel db alter table <tablespace\_name> resize to <new\_size>;".

